                        <h3 class="text-uppercase raleway-sbold">Mission & Vision</h3>
                        <p class="paira-margin-top-1 letter-spacing-2 margin-bottom-0">
                            As lovers of beer and other drinks, the five of us united on a quest to provide everyone with the finest beers, spirits, whiskeys and wines.
                        </p>
                        <p class="paira-margin-top-1 letter-spacing-2 margin-bottom-0">
                            You can share a cold beer with your other half on a starry summer night near the beach.
                            Find a rare Wine with smoky flavor to pair with your gourmet dishes or a sparkling rose to make a toast on your best friend's wedding.
                            Enjoy your Gin & tonic while you reminisce the good old times with your high school friends at your reunion.
                            And don't forget that you can always find time to enjoy an irish Whiskey on ice while you read your favourite book near the fireplace.
                        </p>
                        <p class="paira-margin-top-1 letter-spacing-2 margin-bottom-0">
                            Our vision is to make all of these come true for our customers and continue to unite them with their family and friends.
                        </p>
